    <h1> Adding a image </h1>
    <img src="apple.jpg" alt="apple" width="300" height="300">

    <!-- upload image in your editor(like Vscode) first then only image will be visible in site-->

    <p>If we try to display an image that does not exist, the value of the alt attribute will be displayed instead. </p>

    <!-- src-> contains the path of image-->
    <!-- alt-> it tell us what the image contain if connection get lost aur slow-->
